Package: sshpilot
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: mFat <newmfat@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 1169
Depends: python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-vte-3.91, gir1.2-secret-1, python3-paramiko, python3-cryptography, libgirepository1.0-dev
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/mfat/sshpilot
Description: Modern GTK-based SSH client with terminal integration
 SSHPilot is a modern SSH client built with Python and GTK4 that provides
 an intuitive graphical interface for managing SSH connections.
 .
 Features include:
  * Connection management with saved profiles
  * Tabbed interface for multiple connections
  * Support for both password and SSH key authentication
  * SSH key passphrase handling
  * Auto-detection of SSH keys
  * Visual connection status indicators
  * Full terminal integration with VTE
